metadata.name: M88verse Genesis Collection NFT
metadata.description: M88verse brings you a next-gen entertainment experience beyond compare. Early backers will mint one out of 88 ultra-exclusive 3D custom-designed NFT, each one earning them a utility-enabled PFP with a richly diverse pool of rarity-powered traits and ultra exclusive access and ownership to our new and innovative Web3 portal designed exclusively for the 88 Genesis and 800 Mansion holders.
